
sequenceDiagram
    actor M as Manager
    participant UI as YogaApp UI
    participant API as API Server
    participant DB as MongoDB

    UI->>API: GET /instructors
    API-->>UI: Instructor list for dropdown

    M->>UI: Select instructor, day, time, type, pay rate
    M->>UI: Submit
    UI->>API: POST /classes
    API->>DB: Check for schedule conflicts

    alt Conflict exists
        API-->>UI: 409 with conflicts and available slots
        M->>UI: Select available slot and resubmit
    end

    API->>DB: Save class
    API-->>UI: Confirmation

    M->>UI: Click Publish
    UI->>API: PATCH /classes/:id/publish
    API-->>UI: Class published